4. **Install useful Claude Code plugins**
   - Browse official marketplace: https://github.com/anthropics/claude-plugins-official/tree/main/plugins
   - Install via `.claude/settings.json`:
     ```json
     {
       "enabledPlugins": {
         "commit-commands@claude-plugins-official": true,
         "code-review@claude-plugins-official": true
       }
     }
     ```

